Dialogs.Dialog: あのさ、よく“好きなタイプ”とか、言うじゃん？ ちょっと聞いとこうかなって思って。
●の好きなタイプ？ そうだな、最近は...。
優しくて積極的な子だな
知的で強気な子だろ、うん。
知的は、分かるけど、強気っていうのは？
言いたいことを言うとか、ちょっとキツイことでもね。
おぉ、いいんじゃない？ それくらい激しいほうが。
そうそう！ ガツーンとね。
優しくて、積極的な子だな。
あれ？ なんか、●ヘンな事言った？
でも、なんか拗ねちゃったような...。
リンコが？ なんで？ いつもの冷たくて消極的なリンコじゃん。
▲小早川＊▲って、クールで頭もいいしさ。そ ういうの、好きだぞ。
あれ？ ●なんか、ヘンなこと言ったかな...。
自覚ないってのが、タチ悪い...。
アンタの好きなタイプってさ、どんなだっけ？ ネタとして聞いてあげようと思って。
ネタって...うーん、最近はそうだな...。
クールで物静かなタイプかな
クールで物静かなタイプかな、うん。
なるほど...つまり、補完関係を求めてますな。
うーん...どういうことでしょうか？
つまり、無いものねだりですな。
そうか！ ●が、暑苦しくて鬱陶しいから！
それは、今の▲小早川＊▲みたいな...。
な、なに言ってんの！？ バカじゃん？
乱暴なくらいがこっちも気楽だしさ。
そうかもしんないけど...。
●たち、お互いタイプだったりしてな。
リンコのは...タイプとかじゃなくて、ほら...アレ。
アンタには到底理解できない、複雑な精神運動によって、その、ど うにかなってるんだからっ！
最新の“好きなタイプ”、聞いとこうかなって。
●の好きなタイプ？ そうだな、最近は...。
クールで物静かなタイプかな
ちょっとクールでさ、物静かなタイプ、かな？
だって、だってリンコはさ、てっきり、その...。
ううん。そうなんだ...難しい...。
今の▲小早川＊▲みたいなの、かな？
もう...ちゃんとホントのこと、教えて欲しいんだけどな、リンコ は。
ホントのこと言ってるんだけどな、●は。最近、素直になったなっ て。
そっか...うん。じゃあ、いい。
Okay, I'll work hard as a library committee today.
▲小早川＊▲ is not here... Is she skipping？
What is this？ Am I doing anything bad？
You are. You are skipping the library work.
Just a little bit would be fine, right？ I'm not skipping. I'm just collecting some wisdom.
For what...？ I'm leaving. You'd better go back too.
You are Rinko's ally, aren't you？
No. Just feel like I need someone by my side now. Is that bad？
If something happened, just tell me, okay？
Yeah. Today I'll do my best as a library committee！
Hah... You're just so uselessly lively.
I feel sluggish and I have headache.
You don't have to be that loud.
But you are sick. Let me handle your work today. You'd better go home.
Don't exaggerate the situation. You worry too much.
Geez！ Now I'm really getting headache. I shouldn't feign sick...
Nothing. You're like a big brother who keeps worrying about things！
(I'm not on library committee duty today. I'll just relax.)
As usual, you have too much free time. You look bored.
That's not the case. I also have many things to take care of.
We have chatted for quite a while.
Well, actually, Rinko was also bored.
Eh？ But today is your turn to work as a library committee, isn't it, ▲小早川＊▲？
Speaking of it... Well, I'll skip it then.
But ▲小早川＊▲, you often skipped your work lately.
A penalty for skipping work is prohibition from borrowing any books for one month, you know？
Ouch！ It's not my fault at all！
It's your fault！ You are Rinko's ally, so it's your duty to take care of all the trouble！
Since Rinko says so, it's reasonable！
I got it, I got it. But you should hurry to work. I'll be sure to warn you early next time.
He's here. Let Rinko hide behind you.
(That teacher is in charge of first year students. So, she ran away from the teacher？)
Hey, don't get too close to me！
Isn't it good？ You looked so happy like that...
What？ Seems like you're in hot haste.
Well, isn't it weird that you see me here？
At a flower shop？ It doesn't fit your image, I guess.
At least I use flowers to decorate my room sometimes.
Hey. Is it really weird for me to buy flowers？ You wanna laugh？
▲小早川＊▲ is a girl, after all.
The way you said it isn't that nice, but... It's fine. Hehe.
But I kind of wonder how ▲小早川＊▲'s room looks like.
If you are curious, why don't you come to visit？
(It's so quiet and peaceful at school today.)
It was from the back of that building. I'd better check...
(I feel like I've seen something that I'm not supposed to see.)
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲！ Are you having fun？
Absolutely. You really like cats, huh？
Why not？ They are cute, so I can't help it.
▲小早川＊▲, you're cute too！ Very cute when you're with the cats.
I have to run 30 laps around the track...
I don't know if I can finish this...
Just a little bit more. Keep it up.
Now I feel like I'm in high spirits.
I think you're not interested in sports.
Sort of... That person just now was so good-looking.
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Even a girl also says this, huh？
"Also"？ So you think she's good-looking too？
(I'm done with this shelf. What's next...？)
It's nothing. As a library committee, this is just an easy job.
Well... It's time to go home...
I'm going home. You take care of these returned books.
It's just an easy job, isn't it？
Sorry for taking your time. I have to go.
Did you see it？ I'm not popular or anything.
Hmm？ But you two look good together.
Not really！ Are you an idiot！？ You don't look good with her at all！
Hehe. I'm here to observe. I'll try not to bother you, so can I stay and watch？
Fine. I'm waiting for my mixed doubles partner here.
Hmm？ Then I might be a bother for you. I'm leaving.
What's the matter？ Seems like that girl just ran away.
Okay, I'm done with the trash！
I just walk past. So, you're working here？
▲主人公＊▲. Can you help me here？
Hey, just a moment ago while I was working as a cashier, a customer praised you.
Yeah. She said that you were polite and your smile always made her feel good.
I'll take you to your seat.
I'm not impressed with this waiter's service.
Your grinning face makes me feel sick.
Here. Seems like someone forgot this pencil box. It was on the floor under that table.
Thank you very much. You are so kind.
Hehe. You really work hard as a committee, huh？ You work hard for your part-time job as well.
▲小早川＊▲. Nice timing. Can you take care of this forgotten item？
(She looks so pissed for no reason...)
What should I do with this then？
I'm not your older sister. Don't keep asking me for every little thing.
What are you angry at？ This is not good, you know？
"Thank you very much. You are so kind."
Whatever！ I'm always a mean girl！
(Why was she so mad like that？)
I'd better go. If we get too close, someone might mistake us as lovers.
She really likes to say some surprising stuff.
▲小早川＊▲？ Eh？ How long have you been here？
Long enough to mistake you two as lovers.
If you're with Rinko, we're probably mistaken as brother and sister.
Thanks to you, school isn't a terrible place for me anymore.
That's great then. You must behave even when I'm not here, okay？
Don't act like you're so grown up. You're just like a good-for-nothing older brother for me.
(She is just like a little sister to me...)
Oh, thanks. Do you feel lonely that I graduated？
Haha. Today, you're being frank, huh？
I could change because of you. Thanks.
And I really want you to stay beside me, forever.
But, that's not possible. You just think of me as your little sister and never see me as a woman.
In the end, you are just too dumb！
